h2. ServiceMix 7.0.0 released

The ServiceMix team is pleased to announce the availability of Apache ServiceMix 7.0.0.

Apache ServiceMix 7.0.0 is the first production ready release based on Karaf 4.0.x, which includes numerous
new features, improvements, and bug fixes.

Major dependency versions for this release:
* Activiti 5.19.0.2
* Apache ActiveMQ 5.14.3
* Apache Camel 2.16.4
* Apache CXF 3.1.5
* Apache Karaf 4.0.8

For more information, please see the [release notes|/downloads/servicemix-7.0.0]
